@node Main "MeMonitor - Documentation"

                        'MeMonitor' V2.05

                   Created by Charles-N. Jacob

  MeMonitor is a simple @{" utility " link use} that displays the available
memory (Chip and Fast) like a cardiac monitor.

  The reason I originally made this program was that I needed a
small utility that could display simple graphs showing the memory
available (Chip and Fast mem) when I used graphically-intensive
applications (like web browsers, image processing software, etc.)
and I wanted to see if I would run out of ChipMem (or FastMem).

@{" Install and use MeMonitor " link use}
